snippet.title: Scars Above – Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Scars Above, our sci-fi action-adventure set on a mysterious alien world, is out TODAY! 

Embark on a journey with Dr Kate Ward, exploring a mysterious exoplanet full of unknown creatures!

Available today on PC, PS5, PS4, Xbox Series S|X, and Xbox One!

For more updates on Scars Above, follow: 
https://scarsabove.primematter.gg/
https://twitter.com/ScarsAbove
https://instagram.com/scarsabove
